<text top="613" left="108" width="335" height="15" font="10">After  passing  the  signal  through  a  half  band   </text>
<text top="633" left="54" width="381" height="15" font="10">low  pass  filter,  half  of  the  samples  can  be  eliminated </text>
<text top="653" left="54" width="381" height="15" font="10">according  to  Nyquist’s  rule.  These  samples  discarded </text>
